### Enhancements

* Split `--snapshot installer` into `--snapshot installer-exact` (restores exact installer state, may downgrade) and `--snapshot installer-updates` (keeps installer-shipped packages at currently installed versions, no downgrade). (#121)
* Auto-fallback now prefers `installer-updates` over `installer-exact` when no `--snapshot` is specified. (#121)

### Bug fixes

* `conda doctor base-protection --fix` no longer downgrades installer-provided packages like `mamba` in Miniforge installs. (#121)

